fulltitle: Chico Freeman Interview by Monk Rowe - 1/13/2001 - NYC
description:
Tenor saxophonist Chico Freeman describes his path to a career as a jazz musician,  gigs with Elvin Jones and McCoy Tyner, and shares his opinions on the state of jazz.
